Qwen3-ASR MLX Runtime

This project provides an independent MLX runtime and JSONL bridge for Qwen3-ASR
checkpoints. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by Alibaba Cloud or the Qwen
team.

Qwen3-ASR model names, model cards, and upstream reference implementation are
provided by QwenLM / Alibaba Cloud:

- https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-0.6B
- https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-ASR-1.7B
- https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3-ASR

This repository does not include model weights.
